Donald Miner commented on [high] strange issue with AF. A series of clicks allows me to get autocomplete in AF to go crazy and always cut out some characters on the text, and then when you click go its undefined.: "step1: any normal page <https://edhrec.com/commanders/chainer-dementia-master>
step2: Expand Advanced Filters
step3: Click on [+] to add a 2nd row of in-cards in AF (without adding a card in the first row yet)
step4: Type out "Sword of F" on the first row.
step5: Click on "Sword of Fire and Ice" to autcomplete it. should look fine
step6: Click on the 2nd row of in-cards in AF. It'll send the text back to "Sword of F" -- I've tried several things, it's what you had before you autocompleted."
attachments.text:
step1: any normal page <https://edhrec.com/commanders/chainer-dementia-master>
step2: Expand Advanced Filters
step3: Click on [+] to add a 2nd row of in-cards in AF (without adding a card in the first row yet)
step4: Type out "Sword of F" on the first row.
step5: Click on "Sword of Fire and Ice" to autcomplete it. should look fine
step6: Click on the 2nd row of in-cards in AF. It'll send the text back to "Sword of F" -- I've tried several things, it's what you had before you autocompleted.
